{"type": "article", "id": 59124, "title": "可以挂在餐桌上的餐椅，灵感来自滑板｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-12-09T22:46:50Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 54937, "name": "BREDA"}, {"id": 54938, "name": "Poketo"}, {"id": 54939, "name": "Studio Vit"}, {"id": 54940, "name": "AMLgMATD"}, {"id": 8331, "name": "吱音"}, {"id": 53252, "name": "门朵家具"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 10, "praise_count": 95, "image": "img/article/article_show/20181209183812uWDkvIJ4yelwaVYH.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; background-color: #ffffff} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #262626; -webkit-text-stroke: #262626} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s5 {font-kerning: none; background-color: #ffffff} span.s6 {font-kerning: none; color: #5264a8; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #5264a8} span.s7 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; background-color: #ffffff} span.s8 {font-kerning: none; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #000000} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>卡路里餐椅 by 门朵家具</h3><p>独立家居设计品牌门朵推出新品卡路里餐椅。设计伊始，如何设计出好看又好用的靠背，就是重点。门朵有位设计师，是个滑板爱好者，突然想着以滑板来做靠背，又大又舒展，肯定很舒服。于是整把餐椅的标志性靠背就有了雏形，又宽又大的靠背，曲线流畅，看着舒展，倚着舒服，反复调试的靠背曲线，找到一个兼顾舒服和实用的弧度。</p><p>靠背与后腿连接处，镶嵌撞色木材，增加趣味和灵动性，炯炯有神。软包增加舒适度，冬天也不用单独加坐垫，PU 材质，耐用且耐磨。四脚八叉的形式，纺锤形的椅腿，双侧档的连接方式，大大提高牢固度和耐久度。椅子靠墙放置时，椅背也不会刮到墙面，打扫卫生时，餐椅可以挂在餐桌上。售价 1800 元起，<a href=\"https://item.taobao.com/item.htm?spm=a1z10.3-c-s.w4002-15856540443.15.1cfd7d7dd1Gosx&amp;id=583306156303\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181209184144uqF4dlfxyvLpNZCh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181209184144D0fuhrmMECWkTl4P.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.325967\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181209184144mUq0NwDQMxvEB6Xz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.669444\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181209184145h8oVZQuE2lDFkdBI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181209184145eLXsrFpGzOkyiM8a.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.650926\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201812091841452UOYl6JvCBghKuFZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181209184145BYLZuTteRgPwvcJX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Chips Lamp by 吱音</h3><p>设计品牌吱音推出新品曙片灯。还记得小时候吃的零食吗？设计师把念念不忘的波浪型薯片重现当下。</p><p>独特的波浪纹路，让光反射地更全面、更柔和，或许不是香脆可口，却也秀色可餐了。售价 399 元起，<a href=\"https://detail.tmall.com/item.htm?spm=a1z10.5-b-s.w4011-16671124525.134.2c001abbJlH5SQ&amp;id=582521562439&amp;rn=a838b75dd577dc7481b7acc04864cace&amp;abbucket=4\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181209184500BA0cpj9eZnX5a37P.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.736000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181209184500siGRZQSXN3vup2tl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.583110\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181209184500pkXBslQuPWDtdraZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.641333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181209184500n6U1aGiMgAINO9F2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.008000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181209184500vjQWZ6w8l0KxYtz4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.437333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>WEBSTR Islands by AMLgMATD </h3><p>2018迈阿密艺术周期间，设计工作室 AMLgMATD 在 UNTITLED, ART 展览的中心区域创造了一个公共座椅装置 WEBSTR Islands。</p><p>设计师极具创造性地将古老元素与最近兴起的聚丙烯材料结合在一起，再与铝制框架搭配，算是将常见材料应用到全新形式中。</p><p>古老的草编织带在铝管制成的框架上缠绕延伸，铝制框架表面使用哑光处理，还选择了附近大西洋的色调。座椅底部还设有橡胶垫脚，因而在室内外均可使用。售价 250 美元，<a href=\"https://www.amlgmatd.com/store\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181209184558Hh0mlURVMtPuwA68.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.799511\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181209184558s2tZLw7D0PXmUVyS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181209184558EFvIlcwoYesGO1S0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181209184559APr63xKFpERvZQu1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181209184559N0t34CFs7q2AlZRm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250611\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181209184559vKyAJBRVLsTW80rl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250611\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181209184559wFlC1Amezdc9VGyN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Vessels Collection by Studio Vit </h3><p>伦敦设计工作室 Studio Vit 运用水晶玻璃和骨瓷创造了一系列手工制作的器皿，其设计与材料一样纤薄而细腻。</p><p>Vessels 系列由 MDR Gallery 推出，包括三个酒杯和水杯，两个水晶玻璃瓶，两个茶杯和咖啡杯以及骨瓷牛奶杯或水壶。虽然每件都是独一无二的，并且形状和厚度略有不同，但每个手工制作的水晶玻璃容器都尽可能薄。</p><p>骨瓷精致细腻，这种薄薄的材料试图在饮用时强调“与液体接近的感觉”，改善使用体验。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181209184637UJYqDovZ6kyceRHl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562793\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181209184637abEU73iYn04ZHLrh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.332487\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018120918463721fFczRG0BQCsLTy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.332487\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181209184638X3xa0FWszk14Oqbp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.332487\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181209184638qDdwN8alP0AprnQE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.332487\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://studiovit.se/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Studio Vit</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Spectra Watch by Poketo for BREDA</h3><p>达拉斯手表品牌 BREDA，专注于以低廉的价格提供高品质、极简主义的手表。最近，他们与洛杉矶生活方式品牌 Poketo 合作，推出了限量版 Spectra Watch，聚焦于色彩的表现力。</p><p>男女皆宜的设计采用黑色无缝皮革表带，黑色表壳和表盘，搭配蓝色时针和黄色分针，明丽的色彩既突出了时间的指引性，又诠释出 Poketo 丰富多彩的美学特征。售价 90 美元，<a href=\"https://www.bredawatch.com/pages/poketo?rfsn=1063685.me8h2jh&amp;subid=jpgq56ngt100x1tt05cft\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181209184757PZ9Tx0b32k1By7W4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181209184757NKHUqvYZQgatmp7B.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181209184757e4vpl9rZ0USL6xFn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181209184757WqTc4azxKikCPgVR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018120918475807QhLxTkvXKnYR9V.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181209184758RZ72Wkmq5oEHJ3lu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181209184758liXBTGV4dRNq9byP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}